{"tid":1785703,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"搞大J不如搞曽德成好過啦，今日成篇文撐新彊種族滅絕，直頭申請人權法制裁","createTime":"2019-12-16T14:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T12:44:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4dab22601657173f9c7dadea5e44bebe68043701","tid":1785703,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:55:15.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯⋯<br />\n新疆暴徒只是少數，但敵對力量運用「綑綁」策略，擴大影響。白皮書指出，「宗教極端勢力肆意歪曲宗教教義教規，將極端主義與宗教綑綁在一起，與廣大信教群眾綑綁在一起，與社會生活綑綁在一起，鼓動推翻世俗政權，妄圖建立教法統治的國家。」一批信教民眾「不割席」，便被套上沉重的精神枷鎖。<br />\n<br />\n暴恐過去旅業大幅增長<br />\n<br />\n極端勢力煽動教眾以歪曲的「教規」對抗國家憲法法律，又抵制學習國家通用語言和拒絕學習職業技能，阻止融入正常社會。不少人受「綑綁」，為暴力活動提供掩護。<br />\n<br />\n新疆政府下決心把一批人送進教培中心，裏面有嫌疑分子及已被判罪的犯人。教培方針是「用拉的方式而不是推的方式，用挽救的方式而不是嚴懲的方式」，進行幫教。中心內教授語言、法律知識、職業技能，以及去除極端化等內容。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">上周新疆維吾爾自治區主席雪克來提．札克爾在記者會上表示，新疆堅持依法嚴厲打擊暴力恐怖犯罪，又開展教培工作，實際效果已見︰新疆已連續3年未發生暴力恐怖案件。<br />\n<br />\n雖然國外對新疆教培中心有負面議論，新疆民眾本身則普遍肯定教培工作成效，當地社會恢復安定，各族民眾和睦相處。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2330184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2330184&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7gogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=6b40aecf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2330184</a>"},{"pid":"0ff54783ac7f3b812afed06d16cd4d6ca22f560e","tid":1785703,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:57:26.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標：5萬人聯署</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">依家差2萬人咋！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"49b215f7c271c663d07da2f233fcce48532962ae","tid":1785703,"uid":28432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T15:03:07.000Z","msg":"曾德成講恐怖主義 人唔笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e539f1f65554946e710607a94ec20b00ecafa14","tid":1785703,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:33:20.000Z","msg":"左膠通處智障到 連曾字都打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f73889fd69c6ec0808b2982eea55eec40bf4c6b","tid":1785703,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47910e72354c158c10d2741749f4434002d368b3","tid":1785703,"uid":145592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T04:08:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08fa1ac93c7a3c38a8de21d28ef983bdd37736dc","tid":1785703,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}